    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-3">2026 maturity targets</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-display-md text-cream leading-tight max-w-[28ch] mb-16">
        From pilot to durable infrastructure<span class="text-orange">.</span>
